text: "Who's Zoomin' Who" is a 1985 song by Aretha Franklin and is the title track to her 30th studio album Who's Zoomin' Who?. It went to number 7 in the United States, number 11 in the United Kingdom, number 12 in Ireland, number 23 in New Zealand and number 38 in Australia.
